Subject: Secunia Research: Microsoft Agent URL Parsing
	Memory Corruption	Vulnerability

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 10/04/2007

   - Microsoft Agent URL Parsing Memory Corruption Vulnerability -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

Affected Software....................................................1
Severity.............................................................2
